                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "one with plants",
                            "alt": "one with plants",
                            "game-obj": "Spells",
                            "aonid": 1618
                        }
                    ],
                    "effect": "The tattoo casts  *one with plants* to turn you into a plant before you can be noticed. The duration of this spell is 10 minutes. If you\u2019ve already Activated the tattoo, you can supply a separate casting of  *one with plants* to recharge the tattoo instead of having the spell\u2019s normal effect. This allows you to Activate the tattoo again in the same day. You can do so multiple times each day, but only as many times as you continue to cast one with plants to recharge the tattoo after each use.",
                    "requirement": "You're in a forest or similar natural area",
                    "traits": [
                        {
                            "name": "Concentrate",
                            "type": "trait",
                            "alternate_link": {
